  • Constructor Details

    • VehicleCrash

      public VehicleCrash​(int rowID, int year, java.lang.String severity, int[] injuries, java.lang.String vehiclesInvolved, java.lang.String location, boolean isIntersection, java.lang.String junctionType, boolean isFromSideRoad, int crashDistance, boolean onStateHighway, java.lang.String terrainLevel, java.lang.String roadCharacter, java.lang.String roadCurvature, java.lang.String roadMarking, java.lang.String roadSurface, boolean roadIsWet, java.lang.String trafficControl, int[] speedLimits, java.lang.String lightConditions, java.lang.String weatherA, java.lang.String weatherB, int[] crashObjectsHit)
      Creates a new VehicleCrash object
      Parameters:
      rowID - Unique ID
      year - Year of crash
      severity - Severity of crash
      injuries - Injuries sustained by people involved
      vehiclesInvolved - Vehicles involved in the crash
      location - Location of the crash
      isIntersection - Crash happened at an intersection
      junctionType - Junction type of intersection
      isFromSideRoad - Main car pulled out from side road
      crashDistance - Total distance of the accident
      onStateHighway - Accident occurred on state highway
      terrainLevel - Terrain level (Flat/Hill)
      roadCharacter - Terrain objects on the road
      roadCurvature - Curvature of the road
      roadMarking - Road lines on the road
      roadSurface - Road surface type
      roadIsWet - Road is wet during accident
      trafficControl - Type of traffic controller at the intersection
      speedLimits - Speed limits of the zone
      lightConditions - Light conditions / visibility at time of crash
      weatherA - Weather at the time of the accident
      weatherB - Secondary weather conditions at the time of the crash
      crashObjectsHit - Crash objects hit during the accident
